description: Trent Diesel returns to NK once again, this time with more experience under his belt and a record of 1:0. He is determined to get another win this time, and is ready to take on Patrick Rouge. Patrick is a veteran fighter here on NK, with a record of 4:3. His experience turns out to be no match for Trent's determination and Patrick can not finish the rest of the match. As a substitute, we introduce Alex Slater. Alex stands at 5'9" and weighs in at 185 lbs. He has no professional fighting background, but feels that his experience growing up on the streets of New York City is all he needs to win this match. Will Trent dominate once again or will Alex be the one controlling him in the end?
title: Trent Diesel vs Patrick Rouge - Round 1
